{"tid":932973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"難民闖美墨邊境 不到一天生下美國人","createTime":"2018-12-08T07:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T09:11:39.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d429695a7322cc790ecb1bba11227d9733067fc1","tid":932973,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T07:40:51.000Z","msg":"難民闖美墨邊境 不到一天生下美國人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9B%A3%E6%B0%91%E9%97%96%E7%BE%8E%E5%A2%A8%E9%82%8A%E5%A2%83-%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0-%E5%A4%A9%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%8B%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA-025616082.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%259B%25A3%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2597%2596%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25A2%25A8%25E9%2582%258A%25E5%25A2%2583-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2588%25B0-%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25B8%258B%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA-025616082.html&d=l8LDnSP6m40B1n5xzDpXwbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=f99b9dde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9B%A3%E6%B0%91%E9%97%96%E7%BE%8E%E5%A2%A8%E9%82%8A%E5%A2%83-%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0-%E5%A4%A9%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%8B%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA-025616082.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中南美洲的難民，想盡任何辦法也想逃到美國，就是為了讓以後的生活更好，11月底時一名來自洪都拉斯的女難民赫南德茲（Maryury Elizabeth Serrano-Hernandez），雖然在跨越邊境時遭逮，但隨後她就在美國領地內成功產下自己的寶寶，有望獲得庇護。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，19歲的赫南德茲與20歲丈夫毆提茲（Miguel Ortiz），10月開始帶著2歲的兒子從洪都拉斯出發，一直走到墨西哥邊境城市蒂華納（Tijuana），11月26日時赫南德茲一家人發現絕佳的機會，成功跨過圍欄進入到美國領土。<br />\n<br />\n不過赫南德茲一家人剛爬上山丘就被美國邊境巡邏人員發現，因為拒絕配合邊境人員的要求，一家人全都被拘留，雖然赫南德茲有告知巡邏人員自己已懷有8個月的身孕，但巡邏人員並沒有相信，結果27日時她就開始腹痛，巡邏人員才發現大事不妙，只能把她送往醫院，接著赫南德茲就生下一名健康的小寶寶。<br />\n<br />\n因為小寶寶在美國出生，赫南德茲一家4口最終在12月2日被釋放，目前占住在聖地牙哥，事後將前往俄亥俄州的首府哥倫布（Columbus），希望能獲得法院給予的庇護。"},{"pid":"980d3da189b5c0280b45dd27919a4dcd9a7e5d20","tid":932973,"uid":121146,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T07:42:56.000Z","msg":"送去加州啦屌"},{"pid":"3856879fa6d2b35cb36c63217099df0df59cad3d","tid":932973,"uid":136002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"980d3da189b5c0280b45dd27919a4dcd9a7e5d20","tid":932973,"uid":121146,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T07:42:56.000Z","msg":"送去加州啦屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T07:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c3bf24d49c3f33db0cc5879bec09bfb97a83e7","tid":932973,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T09:07:29.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲"},{"pid":"dbabfb6e5ea0ea8c67372312a0700e5d75f0da70","tid":932973,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"980d3da189b5c0280b45dd27919a4dcd9a7e5d20","tid":932973,"uid":121146,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T07:42:56.000Z","msg":"送去加州啦屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T09:09:36.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"d3985cde046300d07611dfa6ded1d6fcd939db72","tid":932973,"uid":42422,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T09:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i1.sinaimg.cn/ty/o/nfl/p/2010-02-08/1265610260_Nh003B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.sinaimg.cn%2Fty%2Fo%2Fnfl%2Fp%2F2010-02-08%2F1265610260_Nh003B.jpg&h=33318004&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}